{"questionId":"11888","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>This question will diagonalize a matrix and apply this to the transformation of a curve.</p>\n<p>Let the matrix&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"M = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\tfrac{5}{2}}&amp;{\\tfrac{1}{2}} \\\\   {\\tfrac{1}{2}}&amp;{\\tfrac{5}{2}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>M</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mstyle displaystyle=\"false\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n                <mfrac>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </mfrac>\n              </mstyle>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Show that&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}} \\\\   {\\frac{{ - 1}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}} \\\\   {\\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;are unit eigenvectors and that they correspond to different eigenvalues.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {\\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}} \\\\   {\\frac{{ - 1}}{{\\sqrt 2 }}}  \\end{array}} \\right) = \\frac{1}{{\\sqrt 2 }}\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1 \\\\   { - 1}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mo>−</mo>\n                  <mn>1</mn>\n                </mrow>\n                <mrow>\n                  <msqrt>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                  </msqrt>\n                </mrow>\n              </mfrac>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <msqrt>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </msqrt>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;corresponding to <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\lambda&nbsp; = 2\">\n  <mi>λ</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span clas